00:46:13.720 --> 00:46:15.050 line:93%
Don't you get it?

00:46:15.920 --> 00:46:19.289 line:93%
Whatever we say, he won't trust us.

00:46:19.490 --> 00:46:21.760 line:93%
He already has prejudice,

00:46:21.760 --> 00:46:23.490 line:93%
and that happened in front of him.

00:46:24.090 --> 00:46:25.460 line:93%
Do you think he'd trust us?

00:46:25.460 --> 00:46:27.460 line:93%
What do you want to do now?

00:46:27.460 --> 00:46:30.599 line:93%
Do you want to let him misunderstand
and think I'm a psycho?

00:46:30.729 --> 00:46:33.570 line:93%
You want to give in to him
and break up?

00:46:33.570 --> 00:46:35.639 line:93%
Is that why you dragged me out?

00:46:35.639 --> 00:46:37.240 line:93%
Don't you get it?

00:46:38.970 --> 00:46:40.710 line:93%
If Father doesn't stop,

00:46:41.010 --> 00:46:43.510 line:93%
there's only one way to stop him...

00:46:44.309 --> 00:46:45.610 line:93%
from being fooled by that witch.

00:46:46.780 --> 00:46:48.119 line:93%
What would that be?

00:46:48.280 --> 00:46:51.420 line:93%
No matter what happens,
I'm not breaking up with you.

00:46:53.559 --> 00:46:55.789 line:93%
But I lived 30 years without Father.

00:46:57.460 --> 00:46:59.159 line:93%
I'm willing to live without him
again.

00:47:00.199 --> 00:47:01.329 line:93%
Manager Jung.

00:47:01.329 --> 00:47:03.329 line:93%
I gave him the last chance.

00:47:03.670 --> 00:47:06.769 line:93%
It's up to him to grab it or not.

00:47:17.550 --> 00:47:18.949 line:93%
You make the hat...

00:47:18.949 --> 00:47:21.650 line:93%
to live a very long life.

00:47:45.869 --> 00:47:46.880 line:93%
Hey.

00:47:48.780 --> 00:47:51.610 line:93%
Are you showing off
that you're highly educated?

00:47:52.050 --> 00:47:55.019 line:93%
Why would you play
some ghost music like that...

00:47:55.019 --> 00:47:57.749 line:93%
in the house when I'm so disturbed?

00:47:57.749 --> 00:47:58.820 line:93%
Oh, my.

00:47:59.249 --> 00:48:03.590 line:93%
This is a very famous aria.

00:48:03.590 --> 00:48:05.389 line:93%
Puccini's Gianni Schicchi's...

00:48:05.389 --> 00:48:07.800 line:93%
Whether it's Gianni or not,

00:48:08.530 --> 00:48:11.570 line:93%
I'm heartbroken, and it's painful.

00:48:11.570 --> 00:48:13.740 line:93%
Give me some makgeolli to drink.

00:48:13.740 --> 00:48:15.099 line:93%
Make some jeon too.

00:48:15.099 --> 00:48:18.869 line:93%
You have so many wines
in the winery.

00:48:18.869 --> 00:48:21.380 line:93%
Why would you drink makgeolli?
It's not dignifying.

00:48:22.780 --> 00:48:26.150 line:93%
If you burp after drinking it,
it stinks.

00:48:26.550 --> 00:48:28.619 line:93%
If I want to poop and rub it over,

00:48:28.880 --> 00:48:31.720 line:93%
it doesn't matter
because it's my house.

00:48:32.150 --> 00:48:34.590 line:93%
Take out makgeolli
and make some jeon.

00:48:35.159 --> 00:48:36.229 line:93%
Yes.

00:48:45.170 --> 00:48:47.599 line:93%
Think about their future...

00:48:47.599 --> 00:48:49.499 line:93%
and you need to learn
how to bend yourself.

00:48:49.499 --> 00:48:51.369 line:93%
You've been showing off
what you have done for them.

00:48:51.369 --> 00:48:52.909 line:93%
And now you want to ruin everything?

00:48:53.079 --> 00:48:57.210 line:93%
You're just throwing
a temper tantrum.

00:48:57.210 --> 00:48:59.249 line:93%
It's just an old person being
crabby.

00:48:59.979 --> 00:49:02.320 line:93%
Crabby?

00:49:03.949 --> 00:49:08.220 line:93%
What does he know about
the difficult life I have led?

00:49:08.590 --> 00:49:10.659 line:93%
How dare he say that?

00:49:14.030 --> 00:49:15.729 line:93%
That's strange.

00:49:16.429 --> 00:49:18.400 line:93%
It's shocking.

00:49:18.530 --> 00:49:21.940 line:93%
She let everything go
after seeing them happy...

00:49:21.940 --> 00:49:23.440 line:93%
at the pension.

00:49:23.510 --> 00:49:25.440 line:93%
She even cried.

00:49:25.510 --> 00:49:27.679 line:93%
But why would she cause trouble
like this?

00:49:27.780 --> 00:49:29.809 line:93%
I know, right?

00:49:30.079 --> 00:49:32.710 line:93%
She's just making up
weird conditions...

00:49:32.710 --> 00:49:34.949 line:93%
because she has no other reason.

00:49:35.479 --> 00:49:38.949 line:93%
It's not that they're unwilling to
move out of her house.

00:49:39.720 --> 00:49:42.690 line:93%
Living at her house
is already stressful.

00:49:42.690 --> 00:49:44.760 line:93%
So Won, it's good for you.

00:49:44.860 --> 00:49:47.099 line:93%
- Father.
- Am I wrong?

00:49:47.999 --> 00:49:51.300 line:93%
To be honest, if she's that rich,

00:49:51.429 --> 00:49:53.139 line:93%
she needs to be thankful.

00:49:53.240 --> 00:49:55.539 line:93%
If I were her,

00:49:55.539 --> 00:49:58.210 line:93%
I'd build 10 orphanages.

00:49:58.369 --> 00:50:01.909 line:93%
If I have more left, I'd donate one
billion dollars to Seoul Station.

00:50:02.179 --> 00:50:05.210 line:93%
They can help the homeless survive
through this cold weather.

00:50:05.909 --> 00:50:08.650 line:93%
She won't take it with her
when she dies.

00:50:09.249 --> 00:50:12.650 line:93%
Raising a child won't be much.
Why is she making a fuss?

00:50:12.789 --> 00:50:14.990 line:93%
Oh my goodness.

00:50:15.519 --> 00:50:18.530 line:93%
If anyone hears you, Shin Mo,
they'd think you're brazen.

00:50:19.090 --> 00:50:23.030 line:93%
It was our mistake
having a child out of wedlock.

00:50:23.300 --> 00:50:25.999 line:93%
Why do you blame her?

00:50:25.999 --> 00:50:30.139 line:93%
I mean, they are in love.

00:50:30.139 --> 00:50:33.510 line:93%
With this much romance,
everything can be excused.

00:50:35.010 --> 00:50:37.249 line:93%
"If you can make a woman laugh,"

00:50:37.710 --> 00:50:40.220 line:93%
"you can make her do anything."

00:50:41.119 --> 00:50:45.119 line:93%
So Won. If you can make her laugh,

00:50:45.119 --> 00:50:47.159 line:93%
you can make her do anything.

00:50:48.590 --> 00:50:51.059 line:93%
There must be a reason behind this.

00:50:51.159 --> 00:50:53.130 line:93%
You should try...

00:50:53.559 --> 00:50:55.199 line:93%
and solve her problem.

00:50:55.360 --> 00:50:59.999 line:93%
Gosh. Don't try to teach here.

00:50:59.999 --> 00:51:01.670 line:93%
You're such a teacher.

00:51:02.269 --> 00:51:04.510 line:93%
In this house, I'm the truth.

00:51:04.510 --> 00:51:06.240 line:93%
Just do as I say.

00:51:06.340 --> 00:51:09.010 line:93%
Shin Mo, be quiet.

00:51:10.210 --> 00:51:11.349 line:93%
Yeon Ju,

00:51:11.979 --> 00:51:13.979 line:93%
what do you want to do?

00:51:15.449 --> 00:51:17.019 line:93%
Shin Mo is right.

00:51:17.289 --> 00:51:19.190 line:93%
I don't want to fight with Mom.

00:51:19.690 --> 00:51:22.119 line:93%
I want to live with So Won
as soon as possible.

00:51:22.220 --> 00:51:23.490 line:93%
So I'll move here.

00:51:24.729 --> 00:51:28.429 line:93%
I don't think I can raise
Han Gyul by myself.

00:51:29.130 --> 00:51:32.369 line:93%
She always gets me.

00:51:33.070 --> 00:51:35.340 line:93%
They say that we should
strike while the iron is hot.

00:51:35.340 --> 00:51:39.409 line:93%
Now that we're talking about this,
you should pack and come home.

00:51:39.940 --> 00:51:44.010 line:93%
Mrs. Yang agreed.
You should come tomorrow.

00:51:45.110 --> 00:51:48.179 line:93%
So Won's room has been
painted clean,

00:51:48.179 --> 00:51:50.519 line:93%
so you don't need to worry
about anything. Come live here.

00:51:50.519 --> 00:51:51.849 line:93%
All right, Father.

00:51:51.849 --> 00:51:54.519 line:93%
I'll trust you and pack my things.

00:51:56.119 --> 00:51:58.329 line:93%
How about you, So Won?
Do you agree?

00:51:59.699 --> 00:52:00.860 line:93%
I'll deal with this.

00:52:02.800 --> 00:52:04.199 line:93%
Let's go. I'll take you home.

00:52:18.280 --> 00:52:22.050 line:93%
Do you think I'm being crabby?

00:52:22.720 --> 00:52:24.920 line:93%
If you don't know anything,

00:52:25.150 --> 00:52:27.090 line:93%
shut your mouth.

00:52:27.690 --> 00:52:29.519 line:93%
After I let him go,

00:52:29.860 --> 00:52:32.289 line:93%
my life has been a fiery pit.

00:52:32.960 --> 00:52:37.369 line:93%
And now you want Yeon Ju
to go through the same hardship?

00:52:38.470 --> 00:52:39.840 line:93%
I beg you.

00:52:40.400 --> 00:52:44.369 line:93%
Just let go of Yeon Ju now.

00:52:49.710 --> 00:52:51.749 line:93%
What are you thinking about?

00:52:52.210 --> 00:52:54.949 line:93%
Are you worried
because I'm leaving Mom?

00:52:55.280 --> 00:52:56.420 line:93%
You're not leaving.

00:52:56.650 --> 00:52:57.889 line:93%
We're going to live with her.

00:52:58.190 --> 00:53:02.559 line:93%
You're not saying I should
wait a little longer, are you?

00:53:02.690 --> 00:53:04.059 line:93%
I think I know the reason why.

00:53:04.659 --> 00:53:05.789 line:93%
What do you mean?

00:53:05.889 --> 00:53:07.360 line:93%
Your mom doesn't hold grudges.

00:53:08.159 --> 00:53:11.970 line:93%
If she had to give us conditions,
there must be a reason.

00:53:12.199 --> 00:53:14.900 line:93%
What do you mean?

00:53:18.869 --> 00:53:21.840 line:93%
Have you heard of the name
Ha Eun Jo?

00:53:22.909 --> 00:53:24.210 line:93%
Ha Eun Jo?

00:53:25.880 --> 00:53:26.949 line:93%
Who is that?

00:53:27.550 --> 00:53:28.720 line:93%
Your older brother.

00:53:30.820 --> 00:53:31.920 line:93%
What?

00:53:33.559 --> 00:53:35.260 line:93%
I had a brother?

00:53:36.860 --> 00:53:38.030 line:93%
That can't be.

00:53:40.699 --> 00:53:42.300 line:93%
Where is he?

00:53:43.170 --> 00:53:44.599 line:93%
In your mom's heart.

00:53:45.869 --> 00:53:46.970 line:93%
What?

00:53:48.369 --> 00:53:53.380 line:93%
Mungyeong Saejae

00:53:53.979 --> 00:53:58.749 line:93%
Why is there a hill?

00:53:59.880 --> 00:54:05.220 line:93%
The bending path

00:54:05.349 --> 00:54:10.490 line:93%
Raises me up

00:54:21.570 --> 00:54:23.369 line:93%
Gosh.

00:54:28.780 --> 00:54:30.780 line:93%
- Hey!
- Catch me!

00:54:31.050 --> 00:54:32.179 line:93%
Come here!

00:54:32.510 --> 00:54:33.679 line:93%
Be careful!

00:54:34.849 --> 00:54:38.420 line:93%
Live life

00:54:38.420 --> 00:54:41.920 line:93%
Roundly like a pumpkin

00:54:42.420 --> 00:54:46.190 line:93%
Mungyeong Saejae

00:54:46.190 --> 00:54:48.860 line:93%
Why is there a hill?

00:54:49.729 --> 00:54:53.340 line:93%
The bending path

00:54:53.400 --> 00:54:56.769 line:93%
Makes me cry

00:54:57.240 --> 00:54:59.940 line:93%
Ari arirang

00:55:00.510 --> 00:55:03.179 line:93%
Suri surirang

00:55:03.979 --> 00:55:09.079 line:93%
Ara-riga natne

00:55:09.849 --> 00:55:12.349 line:93%
- Arirang
- Mom, I'm home!

00:55:12.349 --> 00:55:13.559 line:93%
I'm here too!

00:55:14.490 --> 00:55:15.820 line:93%
Coming.

00:55:19.599 --> 00:55:23.030 line:93%
Don't they love it?

00:55:23.570 --> 00:55:26.900 line:93%
Your father-in-law
always said he wanted to...

00:55:26.900 --> 00:55:28.539 line:93%
live with you.

00:55:28.840 --> 00:55:31.639 line:93%
Gosh, it's good news for him.

00:55:32.010 --> 00:55:34.479 line:93%
Mom, please don't be angry.

00:55:34.479 --> 00:55:38.010 line:93%
No, I'm not angry. I'm not.

00:55:38.280 --> 00:55:40.519 line:93%
I mean,

00:55:40.619 --> 00:55:43.650 line:93%
my daughter is going to
live with someone she loves.

00:55:43.650 --> 00:55:45.949 line:93%
Why would I be angry?

00:55:46.260 --> 00:55:48.920 line:93%
I mean it. I do.

00:55:48.920 --> 00:55:52.630 line:93%
My biggest wish was that
you'd find someone you love...

00:55:52.630 --> 00:55:54.130 line:93%
and that you'd live with him.

00:55:54.260 --> 00:55:56.130 line:93%
I mean it, Yeon Ju.

00:55:56.130 --> 00:55:59.670 line:93%
So you can take all your clothes...

00:55:59.670 --> 00:56:01.999 line:93%
and the furniture you want
from this house.

00:56:02.099 --> 00:56:05.670 line:93%
And if you need anything else,
you can buy anything.

00:56:05.670 --> 00:56:07.139 line:93%
You can buy everything you want.

00:56:07.510 --> 00:56:10.449 line:93%
I just had a few drinks,

00:56:10.449 --> 00:56:13.119 line:93%
and now I'm feeling dizzy.

00:56:13.820 --> 00:56:16.050 line:93%
You should stay a bit before you go.

00:56:18.820 --> 00:56:20.690 line:93%
You're doing this because of him.

00:56:23.829 --> 00:56:24.929 line:93%
Ha Eun Jo.

00:56:25.729 --> 00:56:26.999 line:93%
Yeon Ju's brother.

00:56:30.470 --> 00:56:34.340 line:93%
Why do you have such a light mouth?

00:56:35.070 --> 00:56:38.139 line:93%
Stop talking nonsense and leave.
I don't want to talk about it.

00:56:41.840 --> 00:56:43.150 line:93%
Mother, please.

00:56:54.159 --> 00:56:55.820 line:93%
I need to talk to you.

00:56:56.329 --> 00:56:58.190 line:93%
Why don't you listen to me?

00:56:58.829 --> 00:57:03.130 line:93%
I don't want to talk about it.
Why do you come lurking here?

00:57:03.300 --> 00:57:04.530 line:93%
I am right, aren't I?

00:57:05.130 --> 00:57:07.699 line:93%
You want us to live separately
because of Eun Jo, right?

00:57:08.099 --> 00:57:10.269 line:93%
You don't want to watch Yeon Ju
raise Han Gyul.

00:57:10.369 --> 00:57:14.880 line:93%
If you know that,
why do you keep talking about that?

00:57:15.280 --> 00:57:17.610 line:93%
You're right. I'm a sinner.

00:57:17.849 --> 00:57:19.820 line:93%
I have sinned.

00:57:19.820 --> 00:57:24.320 line:93%
So I can't bear to watch Yeon Ju
raise someone else's child.

00:57:24.320 --> 00:57:26.720 line:93%
That's why I told you to leave.

00:57:27.289 --> 00:57:31.159 line:93%
It's like torture to me.

00:57:31.159 --> 00:57:32.329 line:93%
Stop it.

00:57:32.829 --> 00:57:34.699 line:93%
You don't need to feel guilty.

00:57:35.499 --> 00:57:37.070 line:93%
You told me...

00:57:37.329 --> 00:57:39.670 line:93%
that you sent your brother away
because of your mother-in-law...

00:57:39.840 --> 00:57:41.570 line:93%
and it happened
while you went to see him.

00:57:42.909 --> 00:57:44.809 line:93%
Anyone would have done it
in a situation like that.

00:57:45.369 --> 00:57:47.740 line:93%
He disappeared while you were
secretly out.

00:57:47.740 --> 00:57:49.309 line:93%
That's not your fault.

00:57:49.610 --> 00:57:52.010 line:93%
That's no one's fault.

00:57:52.920 --> 00:57:54.380 line:93%
You didn't abandon him on purpose.

00:57:54.749 --> 00:57:56.389 line:93%
You don't need to feel guilty.

00:57:57.420 --> 00:58:00.559 line:93%
So, please forget the past...

00:58:01.389 --> 00:58:03.059 line:93%
What if I did abandon him?

00:58:07.159 --> 00:58:09.429 line:93%
What if I did abandon him?

00:58:15.070 --> 00:58:19.780 line:93%
I couldn't... I couldn't tell you.

00:58:21.409 --> 00:58:25.179 line:93%
That's not something
that a human would do.

00:58:25.179 --> 00:58:27.380 line:93%
But it's what I've done.

00:58:27.380 --> 00:58:30.289 line:93%
So I couldn't tell you the truth!

00:58:32.420 --> 00:58:33.619 line:93%
Mother.

00:58:34.360 --> 00:58:35.490 line:93%
Gosh.

00:58:43.170 --> 00:58:44.329 line:93%
I...

00:58:45.530 --> 00:58:46.900 line:93%
Eun Jo...

00:58:48.099 --> 00:58:50.909 line:93%
I abandoned Eun Jo...

00:58:51.510 --> 00:58:55.340 line:93%
on purpose.

00:58:56.449 --> 00:58:59.010 line:93%
I went back home to see my brother.

00:58:59.749 --> 00:59:01.880 line:93%
I couldn't stand watching...

00:59:01.880 --> 00:59:04.820 line:93%
how he was living,

00:59:05.050 --> 00:59:08.119 line:93%
so I abandoned him.

00:59:15.559 --> 00:59:16.729 line:93%
Chun Bum.

00:59:17.030 --> 00:59:18.300 line:93%
Chun Ok.

00:59:20.840 --> 00:59:23.110 line:93%
My mother-in-law promised me...

00:59:23.110 --> 00:59:25.340 line:93%
to send him to a rich family.

00:59:25.940 --> 00:59:28.940 line:93%
But he cut wood in the winter...

00:59:28.940 --> 00:59:30.309 line:93%
wearing worn-out cotton clothes...

00:59:30.309 --> 00:59:33.050 line:93%
and rubber shoes.

00:59:33.720 --> 00:59:35.380 line:93%
They didn't even send him to school.

00:59:35.449 --> 00:59:38.849 line:93%
They made him work
like a total slave.

00:59:39.190 --> 00:59:40.820 line:93%
After I saw that,

00:59:44.990 --> 00:59:48.130 line:93%
I did what I did.

00:59:50.199 --> 00:59:51.499 line:93%
What do you mean?

00:59:52.530 --> 00:59:54.240 line:93%
What did you do?

00:59:56.809 --> 00:59:58.610 line:93%
Tell me what you did.

00:59:58.610 --> 01:00:00.079 line:93%
What did you do?

01:00:13.090 --> 01:00:15.590 line:93%
Hey, kid.

01:00:16.630 --> 01:00:18.929 line:93%
Wake up, kid.

01:00:26.369 --> 01:00:27.900 line:93%
Chun Ok.

01:00:27.940 --> 01:00:29.369 line:93%
Chun Ok.

01:00:30.210 --> 01:00:31.409 line:93%
Chun Ok.

01:00:33.780 --> 01:00:35.240 line:93%
Chun Ok.

01:00:35.780 --> 01:00:37.809 line:93%
What do I do now?

01:00:38.110 --> 01:00:40.479 line:93%
Chun Ok.

01:00:41.420 --> 01:00:43.849 line:93%
What do I do now?

01:00:48.389 --> 01:00:50.260 line:93%
I left Eun Jo there...

01:00:50.260 --> 01:00:53.800 line:93%
and went home alone.

01:00:54.360 --> 01:00:57.729 line:93%
I left him in the train station
and went home alone.

01:00:58.400 --> 01:01:01.970 line:93%
I left him crying on the street...

01:01:02.139 --> 01:01:04.409 line:93%
and went home alone.

01:01:05.539 --> 01:01:06.679 line:93%
Mom.

01:01:09.510 --> 01:01:10.610 line:93%
Since then...

01:01:12.349 --> 01:01:14.420 line:93%
we could never find him.

01:01:15.619 --> 01:01:17.349 line:93%
When I got pregnant with you,

01:01:17.949 --> 01:01:20.690 line:93%
my mother-in-law cursed at me.

01:01:21.490 --> 01:01:23.829 line:93%
If I ever give a birth
to a daughter,

01:01:24.130 --> 01:01:28.030 line:93%
my daughter will pay for what I did.

01:01:28.030 --> 01:01:30.099 line:93%
She cursed at me.

01:01:32.499 --> 01:01:34.999 line:93%
If you raise Dr. Lee's child,

01:01:34.999 --> 01:01:38.340 line:93%
that's all my fault.

01:01:38.470 --> 01:01:40.280 line:93%
You're raising Han Gyul...

01:01:40.280 --> 01:01:44.280 line:93%
because of what I've done wrong.

01:01:44.280 --> 01:01:49.220 line:93%
That's why I can't face her.

01:01:49.220 --> 01:01:52.789 line:93%
I can't. Do you get it?

01:02:00.429 --> 01:02:01.499 line:93%
Mom.

01:02:02.300 --> 01:02:05.070 line:93%
You were suffering so much.
Why didn't you tell me?

01:02:05.070 --> 01:02:06.599 line:93%
You should've told me earlier.

01:02:07.070 --> 01:02:09.139 line:93%
Then you didn't have
to suffer alone...

01:02:09.710 --> 01:02:12.139 line:93%
for all those years.

01:02:15.579 --> 01:02:18.110 line:93%
But Mom...

01:02:18.710 --> 01:02:20.449 line:93%
if that's so painful,

01:02:21.079 --> 01:02:24.749 line:93%
you can pay Han Gyul for
what you did to him instead.

01:02:25.550 --> 01:02:28.460 line:93%
Give the love you couldn't
give him to Han Gyul,

01:02:28.460 --> 01:02:29.829 line:93%
and you can pay her instead.

01:02:30.530 --> 01:02:33.329 line:93%
As long as you and I raise
Han Gyul together,

01:02:33.699 --> 01:02:34.860 line:93%
it's all fine.

01:02:35.929 --> 01:02:38.630 line:93%
As much as we love Han Gyul,

01:02:40.199 --> 01:02:44.139 line:93%
someone else probably loved
my brother.

01:02:45.170 --> 01:02:48.179 line:93%
That will do it. That'll do it, Mom.

01:02:49.139 --> 01:02:50.449 line:93%
Let's do that.

01:02:51.949 --> 01:02:53.280 line:93%
That will do, Mom.

01:03:51.670 --> 01:03:54.840 line:93%
What? Chun Ok?

01:03:55.579 --> 01:03:57.050 line:93%
Say it.

01:03:57.050 --> 01:03:59.110 line:93%
What are you supposed to call her
instead of Chun Ok?

01:03:59.110 --> 01:04:02.479 line:93%
Chun Ok. Chun Ok. Chun Ok.

01:04:02.479 --> 01:04:05.389 line:93%
Mom. It's Mom. Call her Mom.

01:04:05.389 --> 01:04:07.019 line:93%
Chun Ok.

01:04:07.960 --> 01:04:09.220 line:93%
Do it again.

01:04:13.099 --> 01:04:16.869 line:93%
Goodness.

01:04:20.070 --> 01:04:23.210 line:93%
It's fine.

01:04:24.510 --> 01:04:26.539 line:93%
It's fine.

01:05:12.019 --> 01:05:13.389 line:93%
Kim Eun Jo

01:05:17.460 --> 01:05:18.690 line:93%
Eun Jo.

01:05:19.960 --> 01:05:21.829 line:93%
Is that my real name?

01:05:36.979 --> 01:05:38.150 line:93%
Manager Jung.

01:05:38.150 --> 01:05:40.849 line:93%
(Myung Rang forgot the order.)

01:05:43.789 --> 01:05:44.990 line:93%
Sorry.

01:05:44.990 --> 01:05:46.789 line:93%
(I'm sorry.)

01:05:46.889 --> 01:05:48.789 line:93%
(It's Tae Yang's turn
to say the line.)

01:05:48.789 --> 01:05:49.860 line:93%
(Laughing)

01:05:49.860 --> 01:05:51.030 line:93%
I'm sorry.

01:05:51.030 --> 01:05:52.130 line:93%
Gosh.

01:05:52.559 --> 01:05:54.900 line:93%
(Man Who Sets the Table)

01:05:55.059 --> 01:05:57.030 line:93%
Mom. Should I give up
on this marriage?

01:05:57.030 --> 01:06:00.099 line:93%
I can't think of a way to beat her.

01:06:00.099 --> 01:06:01.999 line:93%
Have you forgotten
how Ae Ri's mom died?

01:06:01.999 --> 01:06:03.440 line:93%
We're not bad.

01:06:03.440 --> 01:06:06.110 line:93%
We're getting back what's ours.

01:06:06.110 --> 01:06:07.740 line:93%
This is justice.

01:06:07.740 --> 01:06:10.210 line:93%
You must be happy this time.

01:06:10.210 --> 01:06:13.550 line:93%
I'll make you smile
for the rest of your life.

01:06:13.550 --> 01:06:15.880 line:93%
I'm going to make you pay for it
today.

01:06:15.880 --> 01:06:17.490 line:93%
Exactly as I suffered.

01:06:17.490 --> 01:06:20.990 line:93%
As far as I know, you can never
beat me no matter what you do.

